name: Beeps Boops and Cats v1.11
description:
The year 3299 

Cats living in a cassette futuristic world, aimlessly floating about. 
The hums of computer fans, the twinkle of led lights and purr of felines.

_UNT1L...

The BEEP BOOP continues to grow in numbers and glitches in their programming are becoming more present.
The M30W sense a threat. A new pilot cloning program is initiated entitled the M30W rebellion. 

_MEANWHILE...

As the M30W build their ranks they must continue to live amongst the BEEP BOOP, "peacefully".
but for how long?
